---
// CardInfo component - Story section with timeline
---

<!-- Story Section -->
<div class:list={['lg:grid', 'lg:grid-cols-2', 'gap-16', 'items-center']}>
  <!-- Image -->
  <div class:list={['relative']}>
    <div
      class:list={[
        'w-full',
        'bg-gray-800',
        'rounded-lg',
        'shadow-2xl',
        'overflow-hidden',
      ]}
      style='aspect-ratio: 4/3;'
    >
      <img
        src='/images/table.png'
        alt='Restaurant Interior'
        class:list={['w-full', 'h-full', 'object-cover']}
        loading='lazy'
      />
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class:list={['text-white']}>
    <h2 class:list={['text-4xl', 'font-bold', 'my-8 lg:my-0 lg:mb-8']}>
      The Story
    </h2>
    <p class:list={['text-gray-300', 'text-lg', 'leading-relaxed', 'mb-12']}>
      In the heart of Fayetteville, Arkansas, <span class:list={['font-bold']}>Moonhouse Coffee Bar and Bistro</span>
      comes to life in a charming home with over half a century of history.
      Carefully restored, it preserves its original spirit and the details that
      quietly tell the story of the place.
      <br />
      <br />
      Moonhouse is a tribute to authenticity and community. It's where locals and
      the city's vibrant student life come together to connect, unwind, and enjoy
      a space that feels both welcoming and alive.
      <br />
      <br />
      Every corner reflects our love for stories, experiences, and moments worth
      remembering. Here, good coffee shares the stage with a cold beer, a glass of
      wine, or a cocktail to fit the night. Welcome to Moonhouse, where every story
      is a reason to return.
    </p>

    <!-- Signature -->
    <div class:list={['mt-12']}>
      <div class:list={['text-4xl', 'text-white', 'font-script']}>Moonhouse</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
